{"type":"click","text":"B\n    \n      Turborepo Monorepo — Separate Apps ⭐ Recommended\n      Two Next.js apps (apps/partner + apps/admin) sharing common packages for DB, types, UI, and business logic. Independent deployments on Vercel.\n      \n        ProsClean separation of partner & admin UXShared DB schema, types & utilsPhase 3 white-label = new app in monorepoIndependent scaling & deployment\n        ConsMore initial setup vs single appTurborepo learning curve\n      \n      Best for: 3-phase roadmap with white-label in Phase 3","choice":"b","id":null,"timestamp":1774367523855}
